item.title: Questions :P
item.dc:creator: @SpaT SpaT
item.description:
@SpaT wrote:

i can only help you on last two questions

NEED HP 135!

Okay Go to your sever files and click on characters> Then find the person’s name you want to Change Hp Level

And Scroll down until you see

[SKILLS] character-skill = 0 1 0 character-skill = 1 1 0 character-skill = 2 1 0 character-skill = 3 14 1155 character-skill = 4 1 0 character-skill = 5 1 0 character-skill = 6 1 0 character-skill = 7 1 0 character-skill = 8 1 0 character-skill = 9 1 0 character-skill = 10 1 0 character-skill = 11 1 0 character-skill = 12 1 0 character-skill = 13 1 0 character-skill = 14 1 0 character-skill = 15 1 0 character-skill = 16 1 0 character-skill = 17 1 0 character-skill = 18 1 0 character-skill = 19 1 0 character-skill = 20 1 0 character-skill = 21 1 0 character-skill = 22 1 0 character-skill = 23 1 0 character-skill = 24 35 0

Change the

character-skill = 3 135 9999 Just have it on 9999 Cause if you have it on 9999999 your will not be able to logg in or you will but it will take longer time to log on.

RUNING ENERGY MORE?

[size=15pt]Okay More runing energy[/size]

Go to characters click on any “name” Find this

[CHARACTER] character-height = 0 character-posx = 2143 character-posy = 5096 character-rights = 0 character-ismember = 0 character-messages = 0 character-lastconnection = 193.69.240.24 character-lastlogin = 20090903 character-energy = 100 character-gametime = 0 character-gamecount = 943

And Now find this

character-energy = 100

Change it what ever you want if you want “999999”
DONT NEED TO COMPILE

Thanks

Have a nice day!
